abstract: College Football Roundup; Baylor defeats University of North Carolina, 49-38, in Russell Athletic Bowl in Orlando, Fla; other bowl game scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Johnny Jefferson ran for 299 yards and three touchdowns to lead the No. 18 Bears in the Russell Athletic Bowl in Orlando, Fla.

headline.main: Baylor Rushes for 645 Yards in Beating No. 10 North Carolina
